{"tid":1308291,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"希望大家記住連儂牆只係一個工具","createTime":"2019-07-12T00:40:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T02:06:09.000Z","uid":58676,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"316ed9369d5fe9fe95a91c978a96929ae2981ac9","tid":1308291,"uid":58676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T00:40:11.000Z","msg":"佢既作用係俾一群仲未完全了解發生咩事既人<br />\n用一個溫和既方式去提醒同宣揚呢群人<br />\n我見到好多老一輩都好受落 證明佢有佢既作用<br />\n但正如各位之前整過好多文宣一樣<br />\n發揮過佢既作用就夠<br />\n我認為最近焦點過於投放係連儂牆<br />\n亦因為隨時有廢老廢中襲擊<br />\n令到一群自己人唔知幾時就俾人攻擊<br />\n最緊要係自身安全<br />\n希望大家勿忘初衷<br />\n盡量集中返係我地既訴求<br />\n不撤．不回"},{"pid":"557f90a1ff5614e6bc5bde44516a75aa5408626d","tid":1308291,"uid":58676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T01:30:04.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c9a23b919ecce775f8f3148c0db3616bc7453417","tid":1308291,"uid":58676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T01:30:21.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"cf53e6a593fd1a40bc5a5008e07af65d6ad61e6b","tid":1308291,"uid":58676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T01:30:32.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2d9a7268a4f87e7c3ca3f344238a4388e32bc501","tid":1308291,"uid":58676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T01:30:43.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"87406d437220ee5e7e2d1963fc3b09be0ab1bc36","tid":1308291,"uid":58676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:06:09.000Z","msg":"push"}]}